{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "The importance of prompts in guiding large language models to generate outputs that align with expectations cannot be overstated.",
    "They form a crucial part of applications based on generative AI.",
    "However, this also opens up the possibility for attackers to launch prompt leakage attacks to acquire specific prompts.",
    "To illustrate, consider the case of AI researcher Swyx [40], who successfully obtained commands used by Notion AI for text refinement through a prompt leakage attack.",
    "This incident underscores the vulnerability of AI models to such attacks, highlighting the need for robust security measures to protect valuable information encapsulated in model prompts."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "To illustrate, consider the case of AI researcher Swyx [40], who successfully obtained commands used by Notion AI for text refinement through a prompt leakage attack."
  ]
}